      p.paragraph A woman decides to step out of her modern life and journeys to a remote monastery deep in the Bach Ma mountains of Vietnam, where she lives with a group of monks. Her silent struggle to adapt to the stoic and peculiar setting leads her to a wholehearted search for serenity. 

