      p.title-1 Character
      p.title-2 Blurring The Lines
      p.paragraph The monks' unwavering commitment to their spiritual practice rendered them ideal background actors, seemingly undisturbed by the crew's presence. Their collective essence, marked by a methodical silence and stoic poise, enveloped the set to such an extent that our lead actor seamlessly immersed herself into the scene, both on and off camera, resulting in a method-like approach that brought authenticity and depth to her performance. 

