        p.title-2 Trúc Lâm Bạch Mã
        p.paragraph The monastery's master, a cinephile in his own right, meticulously oversaw the construction of the monastery to transform it into a picturesque masterpiece from every perspective. The symmetrical structures, adorned with intricate detailing, stand in harmonious contrast against the breathtaking backdrop of the natural setting. The beautifully maintained buildings provided an impeccable visual canvas for the film.

